{"word":"G3922 - παρεισέρχομαι - pareisérchomai - par-ice-er'-khom-ahee - Come in privily","slug":"G3922","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παρεισέρχομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pareisérchomai"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>par-ice-er'-khom-ahee"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Come in privily"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C0;&#x03B1;&#x03C1;&#x03B5;&#x03B9;&#x03C3;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C1;&#x03C7;&#x03BF;&#x03BC;&#x03B1;&#x03B9; - pareiserchomai</b> - <i>par-ice-er'-khom-ahee</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>; to <i>come in along side</i>, that is, <i>supervene additionally</i> or <i>stealthily:</i> - come in privily, enter."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G1330\">G1330</a>, <a href=\"#/G1525\">G1525</a>, <a href=\"#/G1831\">G1831</a>, <a href=\"#/G1904\">G1904</a>, <a href=\"#/G2064\">G2064</a>, <a href=\"#/G3928\">G3928</a>, <a href=\"#/G4022\">G4022</a>, <a href=\"#/G4281\">G4281</a>, <a href=\"#/G4334\">G4334</a>, <a href=\"#/G4905\">G4905</a>, <a href=\"#/G565\">G565</a>"}]}